      • getReport

        Report getReport(ReportDef reportDef,
               boolean restrictToToolsInSite,
               PagingPosition page,
               boolean log)
        Produce a report based on supplied parameters (paged results).
        Parameters:
        params - Object containing specific report parameters (see ReportDef)
        restrictToToolsInSite - Whether to limit report to events from tools available in site
        page - Paging information (see PagingPosition)
        log - If true, an event will be logged
        Returns:
        The report (see Report)

      • getReportRowCount

        int getReportRowCount(ReportDef reportDef,
                    boolean restrictToToolsInSite)
        Get row count for a report based on supplied parameters (paged results).
        Parameters:
        params - Object containing specific report parameters (see ReportDef)
        restrictToToolsInSite - Whether to limit report to events from tools available in site
        Returns:
        The report row count

      • getReportFormattedParams

        ReportFormattedParams getReportFormattedParams()
        Return utility class to retrieve formatted report parameters.

      • isReportColumnAvailable

        boolean isReportColumnAvailable(ReportParams params,
                              String column)
        Check if a given column is displayable (has data) for the specified report parameters.
        Parameters:
        params - Object containing specific report parameters (see ReportParams)
        column - Column name (see StatsManager.T_SITE, StatsManager.T_USER, StatsManager.T_EVENT, StatsManager.T_RESOURCE, StatsManager.T_RESOURCE_ACTION, StatsManager.T_DATE, StatsManager.T_LASTDATE, StatsManager.T_TOTAL)
        Returns:
        True if column has data and can be displayed; false otherwise

      • getReportDefinitions

        List<ReportDef> getReportDefinitions(String siteId,
                                   boolean includedPredefined,
                                   boolean includeHidden)
        Load report definitions for a specific site from DB.
        Parameters:
        siteId - The site id or null to load default (global) report definitions.
        includedPredefined - If true, predefined report definitions will also be included
        includeHidden - If true, hidden report definitions will also be included
        Returns:
        A list of report definitions.
